Class BeanMetaFiltered<T>

java.lang.Object
org.apache.juneau.BeanMeta<T>
org.apache.juneau.BeanMetaFiltered<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The class type that this metadata applies to.
public final class BeanMetaFiltered<T> extends BeanMeta<T>
Same as BeanMeta, except the list of bean properties are limited by a @Beanp(properties) annotation.
